/*
 * This Hyperlambda snippet demonstrates how to decrement the value of a node by 1 using the [math.decrement] slot.
 * 
 * 1. [math.decrement]
 *    * Decrements the value of the node pointed to by its expression by 1.
 *    * The expression [x:@.arg] points to the [.arg] node whose value will be decremented.
 */
math.decrement:x:@.arg